source.name: Number of Children Reunified with Families per Year - Oklahoma
source.description: Number of children reunified with families during a state fiscal year - 10 your trend. The data for fiscal year 2004 is a 3-year average due to significant policy change that year. The data includes trial reunification.

datasets.name: Number of Children Reunified with Families per Year - Oklahoma Column Chart
datasets.description: Chart showing the 10-year trend in the number of children reunified with their families. The data for fiscal year 2004 is a 3-year average as the result of significant policy changes that year. The data include trial reunification.
